title: al-Fatḥ al-rabbānī fīmā dhahala ʻanhu al-Zurqānī
Sharḥ Mukhtaṣar ʻalá Alfīyat Ibn Mālik
al-Fatḥ al-rabbānī fīmā dhahala ʻanhu al-Zurqānī
Taḥrīr al-qawāʻid al-manṭiqīyah fī sharḥ al-Risālah al-Shamsīyah
Kāfiyat al-ṭālib al-rabbānī li-Risālat Ibn Abī Zayd al-Qayrawānī. Fatḥ al-mannān ʻalá naẓm mawrid al-ẓamʼān
Manhaj al-ʻilm wa-al-bayān wa-nuzhat al-samʻ wa-al-aʻyān
